<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" class="h-100">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/img/favicon.svg">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <title>Dashboard | Comprobacion de datos</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/general.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/datatables.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/dashboard.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.14.0/css/all.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/animate.css">
    <script src="/js/jq-bs-bundle.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/moment.js/2.29.1/moment.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/fullcalendar@5.3.0/main.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js@2/dist/Chart.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body class="page bg-light d-flex flex-column h-100">
    <div class="modal fade" id="modalCambiarEstado" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel"
        aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header bg-warning">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Cambiar estado de <span id="nombreTarget"></span>
                    </h5>
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                        <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible" style="display: none;" role="alert"
                        id="alerta_error_estado">
                        No se pudo cambiar el estado!
                        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
                            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <span class="sr-only" id="cedulaTarget"></span>
                    Al confirmar el estado de un estudiante, este sera un
                    estudiante que podra matricular talleres de la piscina. <br>
                    Desea cambiar el estado del estudiante a confirmado?
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-warning" data-dismiss="modal">Cancelar</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" id="CambiarEstadoRechazarBoton">Rechazar</button>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-success" id="CambiarEstadoConfirmarBoton">Confirmar</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex" id="wrapper">
        <%- include('menuDashboard') %>
        <div id="page-content-wrapper">
            <%- include('headerDashboard') %>
            <%- include('filterComprobacionDashboard') %>
            <div class="container-fluid mt-4">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-primary my-3 rounded-3">
                    <div class="card-body py-4">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <h2 class="font-weight-bolder">Lista de Usuarios Registrados</h2>
                                <small class="text-muted">En esta seccion se muestra la lista de usuarios
                                    registrados que una vez que completen el formulario <br>
                                    de registro necesitan de una comprobacion por parte de un <a
                                        href="/admin/administradores">Administrador</a>.</small><br>
                                <small>Informacion Actualizada hace: <span class="text-success"
                                        id="infoTiming"></span></small>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col border-right">
                                <h1 class="m-0 font-weight-bolder text-primary animate__animated animate__flipInX animate_delay_t1"
                                    id="usuarios_registrados_stats">0</h1>
                                <small class="text-muted"data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="bottom" 
                                title="Cantidad Total de Estudiantes Registrados en el sistema">Usuarios Registrados &nbsp; <i
                                        class="fas fa-align-center text-info"></i></small>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col border-right">
                                <h1 class="m-0 font-weight-bolder text-primary animate__animated animate__flipInX animate_delay_t2"
                                    id="usuarios_verificados_stats">0</h1>
                                <small class="text-muted" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="bottom" 
                                title="Cantidad Total de Estudiantes Verificados">Usuarios Verificados &nbsp; <i
                                        class="fas fa-align-center text-info"></i></small>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col">
                                <h1 class="m-0 font-weight-bolder text-primary animate__animated animate__flipInX animate_delay_t3" 
                                id="usuarios_nuevos_stats">0</h1>
                                <small class="text-muted" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="bottom" 
                                title="Cantidad Total de Estudiantes Nuevos">Nuevos Usuarios &nbsp; <i
                                        class="fas fa-align-center text-info"></i></small>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white shadow-primary p-3 rounded-3 mt-4 animate__animated animate__fadeIn animate__slow">
                    <div class="row mx-0 d-flex justify-content-between">
                        <div class="col">
                            <div class="mb-1">
                                <div class="input-group flex-nowrap">
                                    <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                        <div class="btn bg-light" id="button_search">
                                            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control border-0 shadow-none bg-light"
                                        onkeyup="searchonfind()" placeholder="Buscar..."
                                        aria-label="Username" id="barraBuscar">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-3 d-flex justify-content-end align-items-end ">
                            <div class="w-100 h-100">
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary mr-2 w-100"
                                    data-toggle="tooltip"
                                    data-placement="top" title="Filtrar" onclick="openFilter()"
                                    id="dropdownFiltrar">
                                    <i class="fas fa-filter"></i> Filtrar 
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white px-0 py-2 shadow-primary mt-4 rounded-3  animate__animated animate__zoomIn">
                    <div class="row mx-0 mx-auto rounded-3 justify-content-between pt-1">
                        <div class="col-md-3 flex-fill d-flex align-items-baseline">
                            <h4 class="font-weight-bold mb-0 ">Listado</h4>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4 d-inline d-flex justify-content-end align-items-baseline ">
                            <h6 class="font-weight-bold">Mostrar</h6>
                            <div class="ml-2 w-100" id="length">
                                <select class="custom-select">
                                    <option selected>All columns</option>
                                    <option value="1">5</option>
                                    <option value="2">10</option>
                                    <option value="3">100</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-3 col d-flex justify-content-md-end justify-content-center align-items-baseline mt-2 mt-sm-0" style="height:35px;">
                            <div id="pagination">
                                <nav aria-label="Page navigation example">
                                    <ul class="pagination">
                                      <li class="page-item"><a class="page-link" href="#"><i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i></a></li>
                                      <li class="page-item"><a class="page-link" href="#">1</a></li>
                                      <li class="page-item"><a class="page-link" href="#">2</a></li>
                                      <li class="page-item"><a class="page-link" href="#">3</a></li>
                                      <li class="page-item"><a class="page-link" href="#"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></a></li>
                                    </ul>
                                </nav>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row w-100 mx-0" style="height: 74vh; overflow-y: auto;">
                        <table class="table custom-table table-responsive-sm table-borderless text-center table-hover"
                         id="table" data-order="[[ 1, &quot;asc&quot; ]]">
                            <thead class="table-light-header">
                                <tr>
                                    <th scope="col">Cedula</th>
                                    <th data-class-name="priority"scope="col">Nombre</th>
                                    <th scope="col">Nacimiento</th>
                                    <th scope="col">Sexo</th>
                                    <th scope="col">Perfil</th>
                                    <th scope="col">Fecha de Registro</th>
                                    <th scope="col">Cambiar Estado</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody id="lista_usuarios_temporales">

                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center align-self-end border-info w-100">
                            <small id="info" class="d-flex align-items-end ml-4"></small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <%- include('footerDashboard') %>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.datatables.net/1.10.24/js/jquery.dataTables.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.datatables.net/1.10.24/js/dataTables.bootstrap4.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/admin/comprobacion.js"></script>
</body>
</html>